start 2016 03 04 2000
end 2016 03 04 2400
status R
description Black Aurora Radar Measurements of energY
contact Mike Kosch
phone 01524-510404
email m.kosch@lancaster.ac.uk
operator Mike Kosch
submitter Mike Kosch
resources UK(12),NO(12)
notes
This experiment seeks to determine the precipitating electron energy spectrum 
in black auroras, the anti-black (white) aurora, and the diffuse background 
using both radar and multi-wavelength optical data. Clear skies are needed. 
Expect cancellations.
